    <p>I was a graduate student in Prof. <a
    href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~dechter/" title="Rina Dechter">Rina
    Dechter's</a> group, working towards a Ph.D. in <em>Artificial
    Intelligence and Machine Learning</em> in the <a
    href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/" title="ICS">School of Information
    and Computer Sciences</a> at <a href="http://www.uci.edu/"
    title="UCI">UC Irvine</a>. I began my studies in the Fall of 2006
    and have successfully defended my dissertation in March 2013.</p>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <hr width="80%">
