    <h3><a name="personal">Personal</a></h3>

    <p>Before coming to UCI I was a student at <a
    href="http://www.rwth-aachen.de/" title="RWTH Aachen">RWTH Aachen
    University</a> in Aachen, Germany and <a href=
    "http://www.chalmers.se" title="Chalmers">Chalmers University of
    Technology</a> in Gothenburg, Sweden, from which I obtained a
    M.Sc. degree in Dependable Computer Systems in 2006.</p>

    <p>I maintain a (sparse) personal webpage at <a
    href="http://www.lotten.net/"
    title="www.lotten.net">www.lotten.net</a>.</p>

